   <text>
      <body>
         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Panesis son of Pakebkis to Dioskoros son of Maron, greeting. I have from you on deposit from hand to hand out of the house, from the public moneys which you administer, 120 drachmas, which I will repay whenever you choose, without any delay or excuse. The fifth year of Imperator Caesar Vespasianus Augustus, Epeiph 4.</ab>
